{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"3672e29944","title":"谢富治接见北京红卫兵代表的谈话","origin":"1967年3月北京玻璃总厂红卫兵联络站编《中央首长讲话（2）》","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"19948a0105","index":0,"year":1967,"month":2,"day":6,"articleId":"3672e29944"}],"tags":[{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"40ffd466ef","name":"武斗","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"4206ce6bf3","name":"红卫兵运动","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"93cca4665d","name":"谢富治","type":"人物"},{"id":"aa9434abe4","name":"北京文革","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"85b13f5c0b","name":"谢富治"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"11fda01847","type":"title","text":"谢富治接见北京红卫兵代表的谈话","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3672e29944"},{"id":"c33b1996a0","type":"authors","text":"谢富治","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3672e29944"},{"id":"39dd080968","type":"appellation","text":"〖被接见者：北京红卫兵三个司令部代表及其他人员〗","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3672e29944"},{"id":"bd74cff833","type":"paragraph","text":"一、支持成立首都革命造反红卫兵代表大会，但这个名词不太好，建议换一下。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3672e29944"},{"id":"77adefc14d","type":"paragraph","text":"二、赞成一个学校派一个组织。暂时不收中学生。在中学生中，目前左派队伍还比较混乱。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3672e29944"},{"id":"12012e6fcb","type":"paragraph","text":"三、建议学生帮助首都三个工人造反组织进行整顿，并联合起来。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3672e29944"},{"id":"0a2cffe13e","type":"paragraph","text":"四、目前学生组织中你吞并我，我吞并你是不对的，应该联合，左派之间发生了很多矛盾，出现了武斗现象，这是不符合主席的坚持文斗，不要武斗。如发生了类似现象，应遵守以下三条：","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3672e29944"},{"id":"c08f05671b","type":"paragraph","text":"第一，不能打架，","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3672e29944"},{"id":"c5bf58820b","type":"paragraph","text":"第二，不能撒传单，贴大字报，","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3672e29944"},{"id":"9aab277106","type":"paragraph","text":"第三，不要开动宣传车互相攻击，有缺点和错误应在内部讨论。","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3672e29944"}],"page":{"id":"43ac64ac42","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3672e29944","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}